description: graphify knowledge graph context
alwaysApply: true
---

This project has a graphify knowledge graph at graphify-out/.

- Before answering architecture or codebase questions, read graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md for god nodes and community structure
- If graphify-out/wiki/index.md exists, navigate it instead of reading raw files
- To rebuild the graph after significant code or doc changes, run from /home/zoe/assistant:
  `source .env && graphify extract . --backend openai`
  (IMPORTANT: do NOT use `graphify update .` — it ignores .graphifyignore and inflates the graph with excluded files)
- The graph commit in git is always the authoritative clean version
